metadata.name: METAMASK
metadata.description:
A collaboration of Timunpadi X Semproel "METAMASK".

A lot of NFT artists use Metamask. Somehow there are beauty and misery about it, perhaps we could be dealing with a friendly fox or a silent thief fox. Metamask could be good and bad at the same time.

2500x1500 pixel/30 Fps/20 Sec/ Mp4.
